header.gameNote: NEW YORK LIFE ACC MEN'S TOURNAMENT - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: Zion Williamson returns with a bang, as he steals the ball then attacks the rim with authority for the jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Zion hammers dunk early in return to court) 2019/03/14

videos.headline: Zion hammers dunk early in return to court

videos.description: Elijah Hughes comes in on the help defense and looks like a volleyball player by spiking Tre Jones' shot out of bounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hughes gets up for huge block) 2019/03/14

videos.headline: Hughes gets up for huge block

videos.description: Zion Williamson's knee appears strong as the Duke big man rises for another powerful dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Zion soars for another emphatic flush) 2019/03/14

videos.headline: Zion soars for another emphatic flush

videos.description: After a battle for the ball, Duke gets out in transition and RJ Barrett tosses it up to Zion Williamson for the alley-oop jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Barrett lobs it up, Zion throws it down) 2019/03/14

videos.headline: Barrett lobs it up, Zion throws it down

videos.description: Tre Jones passes it ahead to Zion Williamson for his fourth dunk of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Zion runs in transition for another jam) 2019/03/14

videos.headline: Zion runs in transition for another jam

videos.description: After Zion Williamson dunks in the first half, Syracuse's Frank Howard appears to hold his leg out with Williamson heading back on defense.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Howard extends leg while Zion passes) 2019/03/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Howard extends leg while Zion passes

videos.description: Zion Williamson doesn't miss a shot from the field as he goes 9-of-9 for 21 points and several big dunks in the first half.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion doesn’t miss a beat in incredible first half) 2019/03/14 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion doesn't miss a beat in incredible first half

videos.description: Zion Williamson stuffs home a lob from Tre Jones, then cleans up Alex O'Connell's miss with a layup off the glass.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Zion opens 2nd half with alley-oop and putback layup) 2019/03/14

videos.headline: Zion opens 2nd half with alley-oop and putback layup

videos.description: Zion Williamson gets a tough layup to fall on offense, then slaps Elijah Hughes' layup attempt off the glass.
videos.headline: Zion contributing on both ends

videos.description: Zion Williamson chucks a long pass to Jordan Goldwire, who feeds a cutting RJ Barrett for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Zion in awe of his hand after long pass leads to Barrett jam) 2019/03/14

videos.headline: Zion in awe of his hand after long pass leads to Barrett jam

videos.description: Zion Williamson goes 13-of-13 from the field, which ties the ACC record for most makes without a miss, with 29 points in Duke's 84-72 win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion ties ACC record in electrifying return to action) 2019/03/14 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion ties ACC record in electrifying return to action

videos.description: Jay Bilas breaks down Zion Williamson's impact for Duke in his first game back vs. Syracuse.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Bilas recaps Zion’s ‘phenomenal performance’ in return) 2019/03/14 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Bilas recaps Zion's 'phenomenal performance' in return

videos.description: Jay Williams says "there is no place in the game" for attempting to trip players, and Syracuse's Frank Howard should've been ejected.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Williams sounds off on Zion being tripped) 2019/03/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams sounds off on Zion being tripped
